<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
<title>Your account · Bayside Pavers</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Onest:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --bp-green:    #5d7e69;
    --bp-green-dk: #4a6554;
    --bp-green-soft: #e8eee9;
    --bp-charcoal: #353535;
    --bp-tan:      #dad7c5;
    --bp-cream:    #faf8f3;
    --bp-bg:       #f4f4ef;
    --bp-card:     #ffffff;
    --bp-border:   #e4e4df;
    --bp-text:     #1f2125;
    --bp-muted:    #70726f;
    --bp-err:      #b91c1c;
  }
  * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
  html, body { min-height: 100%; }
  body {
    font-family: 'Onest', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;
    color: var(--bp-text);
    background: var(--bp-bg);
    line-height: 1.5; font-size: 15px;
  }
  a { color: var(--bp-green-dk); text-decoration: none; }
  a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }

  /* App shell */
  .v2-app { display: flex; min-height: 100vh; }

  /* Sidebar */
  .v2-sidebar {
    width: 240px; flex-shrink: 0;
    background: #fff;
    border-right: 1px solid var(--bp-border);
    display: flex; flex-direction: column;
    padding: 22px 0 16px;
    position: sticky; top: 0; height: 100vh;
    overflow-y: auto;
  }
  .v2-brand { padding: 0 18px 22px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--bp-border); display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 4px; }
  .v2-brand img { height: 30px; width: auto; display: block; }
  .v2-brand-tag { font-size: 10px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.18em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--bp-muted); margin-top: 6px; }
  .v2-nav { flex: 1; padding: 18px 0; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 16px; }
  .v2-nav-group { display: flex; flex-direction: column; }
  .v2-nav-group-label {
    font-size: 10px; font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--bp-muted);
    padding: 0 18px 6px;
  }
  .v2-nav-btn {
    background: none; border: none;
    font-family: inherit; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--bp-text);
    text-align: left;
    padding: 9px 18px 9px 26px;
    cursor: pointer;
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;
    position: relative;
    transition: background .12s, color .12s;
  }
  .v2-nav-btn::before {
    content: ''; position: absolute; left: 18px; top: 50%;
    width: 4px; height: 4px; border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--bp-muted); transform: translateY(-50%);
    transition: background .12s;
  }
  .v2-nav-btn:hover { background: var(--bp-cream); color: var(--bp-charcoal); }
  .v2-nav-btn.is-active {
    background: var(--bp-green-soft);
    color: var(--bp-green-dk);
    font-weight: 600;
  }
  .v2-nav-btn.is-active::before { background: var(--bp-green); }
  .v2-nav-badge {
    margin-left: auto;
    background: var(--bp-cream);
    color: var(--bp-muted);
    font-size: 10px; font-weight: 700;
    padding: 1px 7px; border-radius: 999px;
  }
  .v2-nav-btn.is-active .v2-nav-badge { background: var(--bp-green); color: #fff; }

  .v2-user {
    border-top: 1px solid var(--bp-border);
    padding: 14px 18px 0;
    display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 8px;
  }
  .v2-user-name { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--bp-text); }
  .v2-user-email { font-size: 11px; color: var(--bp-muted); }
  .v2-signout {
    background: transparent;
    border: 1px solid var(--bp-border);
    color: var(--bp-charcoal);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 7px 12px;
    font: inherit; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: background .15s, color .15s, border-color .15s;
    margin-top: 4px;
  }
  .v2-signout:hover { background: var(--bp-text); color: #fff; border-color: var(--bp-text); }

  /* Main */
  .v2-main { flex: 1; min-width: 0; padding: 32px 40px 80px; max-width: 1200px; }
  .v2-pane { display: none; }
  .v2-pane.is-active { display: block; }

  .v2-pane-eyebrow {
    font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase; font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--bp-muted);
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }
  .v2-pane h1 {
    font-size: 28px; font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--bp-text);
    letter-spacing: -0.014em;
    line-height: 1.2;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .v2-pane-lede {
    font-size: 14px; color: var(--bp-muted);
    line-height: 1.6; max-width: 640px;
    margin-bottom: 28px;
  }

  /* Hero (overview) */
  .v2-hero {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--bp-green) 0%, var(--bp-green-dk) 100%);
    color: #fff;
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 32px 36px 28px;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    box-shadow: 0 12px 32px rgba(93, 126, 105, 0.18);
  }
  .v2-hero-greet { font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 0.2em; text-transform: uppercase; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.72); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .v2-hero h2 { font-size: 24px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: -0.012em; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .v2-hero p { font-size: 14px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.84); line-height: 1.55; max-width: 620px; }
  .v2-hero-cta {
    display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
    background: #fff; color: var(--bp-green-dk);
    padding: 10px 18px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600;
    text-decoration: none;
    margin-top: 16px;
    transition: transform .15s, box-shadow .15s;
  }
  .v2-hero-cta:hover { transform: translateY(-1px); box-shadow: 0 8px 18px rgba(0,0,0,0.16); text-decoration: none; }

  /* Stat cards */
  .v2-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(280px, 1fr)); gap: 14px; margin-bottom: 24px; }
  .v2-stat {
    background: #fff;
    border: 1px solid var(--bp-border);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 18px 20px;
  }
  .v2-stat-label { font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: 0.14em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--bp-muted); font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .v2-stat-val { font-size: 22px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--bp-text); letter-spacing: -0.012em; }
  .v2-stat-sub { font-size: 12px; color: var(--bp-muted); margin-top: 4px; }

  /* Action cards */
  .v2-actions { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(220px, 1fr)); gap: 12px; margin-bottom: 24px; }
  .v2-action {
    background: #fff;
    border: 1px solid var(--bp-border);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 16px 18px;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: inherit;
    display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 6px;
    transition: border-color .15s, transform .15s, box-shadow .15s;
  }
  .v2-action:hover { border-color: var(--bp-green); transform: translateY(-1px); box-shadow: 0 4px 14px rgba(93,126,105,0.10); text-decoration: none; }
  .v2-action-title { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--bp-text); display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; }
  .v2-action-desc { font-size: 12px; color: var(--bp-muted); line-height: 1.5; }
  .v2-action-icon { font-size: 16px; }

  /* Proposal cards */
  .v2-prop-card {
    background: #fff;
    border: 1px solid var(--bp-border);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 20px 22px;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }
  .v2-prop-head { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: flex-start; gap: 12px; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-bottom: 14px; }
  .v2-prop-head-info { flex: 1; min-width: 200px; }
  .v2-prop-addr { font-size: 17px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--bp-text); line-height: 1.3; margin-bottom: 2px; }
  .v2-prop-meta { font-size: 12px; color: var(--bp-muted); }
  .v2-prop-total { font-size: 24px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--bp-green-dk); letter-spacing: -0.012em; white-space: nowrap; }
  .v2-prop-status {
    display: inline-block; padding: 3px 10px;
    border-radius: 999px; font-size: 10px; font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em; text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .v2-prop-status.draft { background: var(--bp-cream); color: var(--bp-muted); }
  .v2-prop-status.sent  { background: #eaf2ec; color: var(--bp-green-dk); }
  .v2-prop-status.signed { background: var(--bp-green); color: #fff; }
  .v2-prop-actions { display: flex; gap: 8px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .v2-btn {
    display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px;
    padding: 9px 14px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600;
    text-decoration: none;
    cursor: pointer; font-family: inherit;
    border: 1px solid transparent;
    transition: background .15s, color .15s, border-color .15s;
  }
  .v2-btn-primary { background: var(--bp-green); color: #fff; }
  .v2-btn-primary:hover { background: var(--bp-green-dk); text-decoration: none; }
  .v2-btn-ghost { background: #fff; color: var(--bp-charcoal); border-color: var(--bp-border); }
  .v2-btn-ghost:hover { background: var(--bp-cream); border-color: var(--bp-green); color: var(--bp-green-dk); text-decoration: none; }
  .v2-btn:disabled { opacity: 0.5; cursor: not-allowed; }

  /* Empty states */
  .v2-empty {
    background: #fff;
    border: 1px dashed var(--bp-border);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 38px 28px;
    text-align: center;
    color: var(--bp-muted);
  }
  .v2-empty-icon { font-size: 36px; margin-bottom: 12px; color: var(--bp-green); opacity: 0.6; }
  .v2-empty h3 { font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--bp-text); margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .v2-empty p { font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6; max-width: 420px; margin: 0 auto 18px; }

  .v2-loading { text-align: center; padding: 36px; color: var(--bp-muted); font-size: 13px; }
  .v2-error-msg { background: #fef2f2; color: var(--bp-err); border: 1px solid #fecaca; border-radius: 8px; padding: 12px 16px; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 18px; }

  /* Quality standards accordions */
  .ho-qs-card { background: #fff; border: 1px solid var(--bp-border); border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden; margin-bottom: 10px; transition: border-color .15s; }
  .ho-qs-card:hover { border-color: var(--bp-green); }
  .ho-qs-card[open] { border-color: var(--bp-green); }
  .ho-qs-summary { list-style: none; cursor: pointer; padding: 18px 22px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 14px; user-select: none; }
  .ho-qs-summary::-webkit-details-marker { display: none; }
  .ho-qs-num { flex-shrink: 0; width: 32px; height: 32px; border-radius: 8px; background: var(--bp-green-soft); color: var(--bp-green-dk); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.04em; }
  .ho-qs-card[open] .ho-qs-num { background: var(--bp-green); color: #fff; }
  .ho-qs-title-wrap { flex: 1; min-width: 0; }
  .ho-qs-title { font-size: 15px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--bp-text); line-height: 1.3; }
  .ho-qs-tagline { font-size: 12px; color: var(--bp-muted); margin-top: 2px; }
  .ho-qs-arrow { flex-shrink: 0; color: var(--bp-muted); font-size: 18px; transition: transform .2s; }
  .ho-qs-card[open] .ho-qs-arrow { transform: rotate(90deg); color: var(--bp-green-dk); }
  .ho-qs-body { padding: 0 22px 22px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.7; color: var(--bp-charcoal); }
  .ho-qs-body p { margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .ho-qs-body p:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
  .ho-qs-warranty-cta { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; margin-top: 14px; padding: 9px 16px; background: var(--bp-green); color: #fff; border-radius: 8px; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none; transition: background .15s, transform .15s; }
  .ho-qs-warranty-cta:hover { background: var(--bp-green-dk); transform: translateY(-1px); text-decoration: none; }

  /* Refer & earn */
  .v2-credit-card { background: #fff; border: 1px solid var(--bp-border); border-radius: 12px; padding: 26px 28px; max-width: 540px; margin-bottom: 24px; }
  .v2-credit-eyebrow { font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 0.18em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--bp-muted); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; }
  .v2-credit-amount { font-size: 32px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--bp-green-dk); letter-spacing: -0.018em; margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .v2-credit-cap { font-size: 13px; color: var(--bp-muted); margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .v2-credit-bar { background: var(--bp-cream); border-radius: 999px; height: 8px; overflow: hidden; margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .v2-credit-bar-fill { background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--bp-green) 0%, var(--bp-green-dk) 100%); height: 100%; border-radius: 999px; transition: width .4s ease; }
  .v2-credit-desc { font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.55; color: var(--bp-charcoal); margin-bottom: 18px; }

  /* Schedule pane */
  .v2-schedule-card {
    background: #fff;
    border: 1px solid var(--bp-border);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 32px;
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 540px;
  }
  .v2-schedule-card h2 { font-size: 20px; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .v2-schedule-card p { font-size: 14px; color: var(--bp-muted); margin-bottom: 18px; }

  /* Mobile */
  @media (max-width: 760px) {
    .v2-app { flex-direction: column; }
    .v2-sidebar { width: 100%; height: auto; position: relative; padding: 16px 0; }
    .v2-nav { padding: 12px 0; }
    .v2-main { padding: 24px 16px 60px; }
    .v2-pane h1 { font-size: 22px; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="v2-app">

  <aside class="v2-sidebar">
    <div class="v2-brand">
      <img src="https://baysidepavers.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/baysidepavers-logo-light-scaled.png" alt="Bayside Pavers">
      <div class="v2-brand-tag">Your Account</div>
    </div>

    <nav class="v2-nav" id="v2-nav">
      <div class="v2-nav-group">
        <div class="v2-nav-group-label">Your Project</div>
        <button type="button" class="v2-nav-btn is-active" data-pane="overview">Overview</button>
        <button type="button" class="v2-nav-btn" data-pane="proposal">Proposal<span class="v2-nav-badge" id="v2-prop-badge"></span></button>
        <button type="button" class="v2-nav-btn" data-pane="war-room">War room</button>
      </div>
      <div class="v2-nav-group">
        <div class="v2-nav-group-label">Actions</div>
        <button type="button" class="v2-nav-btn" data-pane="print">Print to mark up</button>
        <button type="button" class="v2-nav-btn" data-pane="schedule">Schedule a call</button>
      </div>
      <div class="v2-nav-group">
        <div class="v2-nav-group-label">Library</div>
        <button type="button" class="v2-nav-btn" data-pane="how-we-install">How we install</button>
        <button type="button" class="v2-nav-btn" data-pane="materials">Materials catalog</button>
      </div>
      <div class="v2-nav-group">
        <div class="v2-nav-group-label">Earn</div>
        <button type="button" class="v2-nav-btn" data-pane="refer">Refer &amp; earn</button>
      </div>
    </nav>

    <div class="v2-user">
      <div class="v2-user-name" id="v2-user-name">…</div>
      <div class="v2-user-email" id="v2-user-email"></div>
      <button type="button" class="v2-signout" id="v2-signout">Sign out</button>
    </div>
  </aside>

  <main class="v2-main">

    <div id="v2-error-banner" class="v2-error-msg" style="display:none;"></div>

    <!-- Pane · Overview -->
    <section class="v2-pane is-active" data-pane="overview">
      <div class="v2-pane-eyebrow">Overview</div>
      <h1 id="v2-overview-greeting">Welcome</h1>
      <p class="v2-pane-lede">Your project lives here. Below is your most recent proposal, your quick actions, and links to everything else.</p>

      <div class="v2-hero">
        <div class="v2-hero-greet">Next step</div>
        <h2 id="v2-hero-title">Loading…</h2>
        <p id="v2-hero-body">We'll pull your latest proposal and current status here.</p>
        <a class="v2-hero-cta" id="v2-hero-cta" href="#" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="display:none;">📅 Schedule a free design appointment</a>
      </div>

      <div class="v2-grid" id="v2-overview-stats"></div>

      <div class="v2-actions">
        <a class="v2-action" href="#" data-jump-pane="proposal">
          <div class="v2-action-title"><span class="v2-action-icon">📋</span> Your proposal</div>
          <div class="v2-action-desc">Full bid, line items, materials, and timeline.</div>
        </a>
        <a class="v2-action" href="#" data-jump-pane="war-room">
          <div class="v2-action-title"><span class="v2-action-icon">💬</span> War room</div>
          <div class="v2-action-desc">Direct line to your designer — chat, photos, requests.</div>
        </a>
        <a class="v2-action" href="#" data-jump-pane="print">
          <div class="v2-action-title"><span class="v2-action-icon">🖨️</span> Print to mark up</div>
          <div class="v2-action-desc">Print your plan, sketch changes by hand, send back.</div>
        </a>
        <a class="v2-action" href="#" data-jump-pane="schedule">
          <div class="v2-action-title"><span class="v2-action-icon">📅</span> Schedule a call</div>
          <div class="v2-action-desc">Pick a time with your designer.</div>
        </a>
        <a class="v2-action" href="#" data-jump-pane="how-we-install">
          <div class="v2-action-title"><span class="v2-action-icon">📚</span> How we install</div>
          <div class="v2-action-desc">5-phase process, videos, catalogs by project type.</div>
        </a>
        <a class="v2-action" href="#" data-jump-pane="refer">
          <div class="v2-action-title"><span class="v2-action-icon">🎁</span> Refer &amp; earn</div>
          <div class="v2-action-desc">$500 off for you and a neighbor.</div>
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Pane · Proposal -->
    <section class="v2-pane" data-pane="proposal">
      <div class="v2-pane-eyebrow">Your project plan</div>
      <h1>Proposals</h1>
      <p class="v2-pane-lede">Your full Bayside proposal — totals, line items, materials, schedule. Use the buttons on each card to request a redesign, swap materials, or print to mark up.</p>
      <div id="v2-prop-area"><div class="v2-loading">Loading your proposals…</div></div>
    </section>

    <!-- Pane · War room -->
    <section class="v2-pane" data-pane="war-room">
      <div class="v2-pane-eyebrow">War room</div>
      <h1>Direct line to your designer</h1>
      <p class="v2-pane-lede">Questions, requests, photos, or just a quick check-in — your designer responds within one business day.</p>
      <div id="ho-chat-section"></div>
    </section>

    <!-- Pane · Print -->
    <section class="v2-pane" data-pane="print">
      <div class="v2-pane-eyebrow">Print to mark up</div>
      <h1>Print and mark up your plan</h1>
      <p class="v2-pane-lede">Print a marked-up-ready copy of your plan, draw notes by hand, and snap a photo back to your designer in the War room.</p>
      <div id="v2-print-area"><div class="v2-loading">Loading proposals…</div></div>
    </section>

    <!-- Pane · Schedule -->
    <section class="v2-pane" data-pane="schedule">
      <div class="v2-pane-eyebrow">Schedule a call</div>
      <h1>Talk to your designer</h1>
      <p class="v2-pane-lede">Pick a time that works. Free, no obligation, on Zoom or in your yard.</p>
      <div class="v2-schedule-card">
        <h2>Book a 30-minute design call</h2>
        <p>Discuss your project, materials, timing, and next steps with a Bayside designer.</p>
        <a class="v2-btn v2-btn-primary" id="v2-schedule-cta" href="https://baysidepaversfreeconsultation.as.me/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="padding:12px 24px;font-size:13px;">📅 Open the booking calendar →</a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Pane · How we install -->
    <section class="v2-pane" data-pane="how-we-install">
      <div class="v2-pane-eyebrow">Library</div>
      <h1>How we install</h1>
      <p class="v2-pane-lede">Our 5-phase quality standard plus deep dives by project type — pavers, driveways, pool decks, walls, turf, drainage, fire features, lighting. Videos, catalogs, and cutsheets included.</p>

      <section id="how-we-build">
        <details class="ho-qs-card">
          <summary class="ho-qs-summary">
            <span class="ho-qs-num">01</span>
            <span class="ho-qs-title-wrap">
              <span class="ho-qs-title">Site preparation</span>
              <span class="ho-qs-tagline">Where every long-lasting hardscape begins</span>
            </span>
            <span class="ho-qs-arrow">›</span>
          </summary>
          <div class="ho-qs-body">
            <p>Before a single paver lands, we set the stage. Our crew excavates to the right depth for your soil type and project category — patios, driveways, and pool decks each have their own minimum specs. We mark utilities, set up edge lines, and confirm grading so water flows away from your house, not toward it.</p>
            <p>This is the unglamorous part of the project, but it's the difference between a hardscape that looks great for 5 years and one that looks great for 30. Most failures we get called in to fix come from someone skipping this phase.</p>
          </div>
        </details>
